      "created_at": "2019-03-21T22:56:48.640Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Shif psh I moth, kjo vajza e ka perzone Marlonin dhe ka perqafu krishterimin. Cfare keshille ke per kete?</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox whitelistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://assets.guim.co.uk/images/favicons/46bd2faa1ab438684a6d4528a655a8bd/32x32.ico\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2019/mar/21/gay-christian-church-lgbt\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"07:37PM - 21 March 2019\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">the Guardian – 21 Mar 19</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:800/420;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8e95a9053f9e3579371a1a1be7a787286571532c.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2019/mar/21/gay-christian-church-lgbt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Being a gay Christian can be hurtful and gruelling. But I refuse to lose faith...</a></h3>\n\n<p>I can face discrimination from both sides, but the church and the LGBT+ community have more in common than they think, says journalism student Lucy Knight</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
